### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/health

### Request OTP (use DEV_OTP in .env for local)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{"phone": "+233200000002"}

### Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{"phone": "+233200000002", "code": "123456", "fullName": "Kofi Buyer"}

### Me (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Search parts
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/parts?q=alt&make=Toyota&year=2015&sort=price_asc
